            </CardDescription>
          </CardHeader>
          <CardContent className="space-y-4">
            <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <p>
                <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-200"
                  >Panoptes:</strong
                >
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400"
                  ><span class="lang-en"
                    >Captures full before/after payloads, parameters, and
                    user/session context.</span
                  ><span class="lang-es"
                    >Captura payloads before/after, parámetros y contexto de
